<style>
  .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
    width: calc(100% - 710px);
  }
  .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
    width: 660px;
    height: 560px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 11px;
  }
  .text-image-block_wrapp-image-border {
    border: 1px solid #3C1F1B;
  }
  .text-image-block_wrapp-image-small {
    height: 440px;
  }
  .text-image-block_wrapp-image-contain {
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
      width: 550px;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
        width: calc(100% - 600px);
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .text-image-block_wrapp {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text, .text-image-block_wrapp-text h2, .text-image-block_wrapp-text h3 {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .text-image-block .rebranding_container {
      padding: 0;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
      padding: 0 15px;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text p {
      text-align: justify;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 0;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image-small {
      height: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="rebranding_container">
  <div class="text-image-block_wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-center-sb">
    <div class="text-image-block_wrapp-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <h2 class="h2-heading-ss w-100">
        <span class="h2-heading-pp">
          Authenticating 
        </span>
        Gucci bags
      </h2>
      <p class="body-text">
        Authenticating a Gucci bag requires a meticulous examination of the bag’s materials, craftsmanship, and hardware. One important aspect to consider is the dust bag, which can help distinguish between genuine and counterfeit products. Gucci is renowned for using only the highest quality materials and ensuring meticulous craftsmanship in their handbags. 
<br><br>
The luxurious feel of Gucci’s materials, such as GG monogram canvas, Guccissima leather, calf or suede leather, and exotic crocodile skins, should be immediately apparent. Counterfeit bags often use cheap leather that looks, feels, and even smells unnatural. The quality of an authentic Gucci bag should be obvious at first sight and touch, making it a key factor in the authentication process.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img class="text-image-block_wrapp-image text-image-block_wrapp-image-contain text-image-block_wrapp-image-border" src="{{ "gucci-seo_authenticating.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Authenticating Gucci bags">
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "SEO Text & image",
    "class": "text-image-block rebranding-wider-section-bottom rebranding-wider-section-bottom-image",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}